quran[20]{c,v,t}:
  44,40,"Ruri! Letsatsi la Tlhopho ke nako e hlomamiselitsoeng bona bohle, –"
  44,41,"Ka Letsatsi leo ho se nang hoba le mots’ireletsi ea tlang ho ba emela, kapa hona ho ba thusa"
  44,42,"Kantle le ba tla amohela Mahau oa Allah: Hobane Ke Eena Ea Matla Oohle, Ea Mohau o Khaphatsehang"
  44,43,Ruri Sefate sa Zaqqum
  44,44,E tla ba lijo tsa Baetsalibe
  44,45,"Joaloka lesheleshele la koporo, le tla beng le bela ka har’a limpa tsa bona"
  44,46,Joaloka ho bela ha metsi
  44,47,"(Lentsoe le tla hoelehetsa): “Mo ts’oare o mo hulele har’a Lelakabe la Lihele"
  44,48,“Joale o mo ts’ele ka Kotlo ea Metsi a Belang hloohong
  44,49,"“Latsoa sena! Ruri! O ne o le matla, o hlompheha"
  44,50,“Ruri sena ke seo o neng o ena le khoao ka sona.”
  44,51,"Haele ba lokileng, ba tla ba maemong a ts’ireletsehileng"
  44,52,Har’a Lirapa le Liliba
  44,53,"Ba apere silika le masela a nonofetseng, ba shebane"
  44,54,"Ho tla ba joalo. Re tla ba nyalisa Balekane, ba mahlo a phatsimang"
  44,55,Kamoo teng ba tla ja litholoana tsohle tsa mefuta ka khotso le bolokolohi
  44,56,"Kapa hona ho ang’oa ke lefu, ntle le lefu la pele; U tla ba ts’ireletsa Kahlolong ea Mollo oa Lihele"
  44,57,E le nala ho tsoa ho Mong`a hau. Seo e tla be e le katleho e babatsehang
  44,58,"Ruri, Re hlakisitse (Qura’n), ka leleme la hau, hore ba tle ba utloe"
  44,59,"Kahoo leta, u talime; hobane le bona ba letile"